bined with other agents that can cause hypomagnesemia such as diuretics, aminoglycosides, cation exchange resins, amphotericin B, cetuximab, cisplatin, cyclosporine, foscarnet, panitumumab, pentamidine, and tacrolimus.', NULL, NULL, 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic');
